com.smartnsoft.droid4me.analytics

Annotation Type AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsDisabledLoggerAnnotation


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public static @interface AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsDisabledLoggerAnnotation
    An annotation which enables to express that an entity, usually an Activity or a Fragment, does not wish to report any analytics usage.

    Use this annotation, when you do not want the underlying entity to report any activity.

    See Also:
    AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLogger, AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsTagLoggerAnnotation, AnalyticsLogger.AnalyticsEnabledLoggerAnnotation
